# Property X Factors Australia

A local Windows-friendly property search dashboard for Australian coastal properties.

Open `Start Property X Factors.cmd`. It starts the local server that powers the manual `Search now` button.

The app has 277 curated beachfront or beach-position records using direct listing pages, with 259 currently visible active listings. Sold, under-offer, under-contract, withdrawn, off-market, or leased records are hidden automatically. The app does not scrape portal search pages in the browser.


